playstore_details.title: Dfox-Crypto Wallet and DeFi Portfolio
playstore_details.description:
Dfox is a chain-agnostic crypto portfolio tracker. It enables you to see all your crypto finances in one place, auto-track and manage cryptocurrencies, digital collectibles and DeFi assets. It is a must-have for cryptocurrency investors.

【Key features】

**Track your crypto portfolio**

- Manage multiple wallets and DeFi assets in one place, automatically sync wallet balance, token holdings, non-fungible tokens（NFTs）and transactions records.

- Support multiple public chains, Bitcoin, Ethereum, EOS and more to come.

- Track prices of over 5,000 cryptocurrencies such as Bitcoin (BTC) , Ethereum (ETH) , Tether (USDT) , ChainLink (LINK) , Binance Coin (BNB) , OKB (OKB) , Huobi Token (HT) and popular DeFi tokens such as Uniswap (UNI) , Maker (MRK) , Aave (Lend) , Synthetix (SNX) , Basic Attention Token (BAT) , 0x (ZRX) , Kyber (KNC), Band Protocol (BAND) &many more.

- Track and showcase your crypto collectibles and non-fungible tokens (NFTs). Support Ethereum ERC721 and ERC1155 assets; EOS Simple Assets and Atomic Assets. View popular digital assets such as Axies, CryptoKitties,Sandbox,Decentraland, Rarible，SuperRare&many more.

**View and Manage DeFi Assets**

- Discover leading Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain and EOS DeFi Protocols and platforms. Monitor your DeFi assets, view deposits, debt, liquidity pools and yield farming activities.

- Support popular Ethereum DeFi protocols, such as Compound Finance, Uniswap, AAVE, MakerDao,Curve,SushiSwap, dYdX, Synthetix

- Support popular BSC DeFi protocols, such as PancakeSwap, Venus, autofarm, BakerySwap, Beef.finance, ACryptoS

- Support popular EOS DeFi protocols, such as DeFibox, Defis.network, PIZZA, Dolphinswap, Organix(OGX),YFC, TIME

**Auto-Sync your transactions**

- Connect your Bitcoin, Ethereum, BSC wallets to auto-sync all historical transactions.

- Support watching and tracking decentralized wallet, use your public wallet addresses from Trust Wallet, MetaMask，imToken，Tokenpocket, Bitpie, Math Wallet, Bread Wallet, Bixin Wallet, Cobo, Blockchain Wallet and other decentralized wallet.

**Powerful Analytics**

- Organize income & expense automatically by date, account and asset.

- In-depth portfolio insights, show your asset allocation, asset and debt positions and etc.

- Visualize your crypto finances with over 50 key metrics and trends, such as balance trend, transaction trend, large transactions and more.

**Real-time Price Updates**

- Track real-time price of your favorite cryptocurrencies such as Bitcoin, Ethereum, XRP, USDT, LINK, Bitcoin Cash, Litcoin, Cardano, Tron, ETC, EOS, Monero, ATOM, NEO, Polkdot and other coins & tokens.

- Support latest price, price trend, 24hchange, market cap, circulation, total supply, 24h high&low price.

- Support on-chain data including total active users, daily active users, on-chain txn volume and value.

- Add favorite tokens to watchlist to stay informed.

**Secure and Private**

- Support no login mode, all your data is stored locally on device. Stay anonymous to maximum your privacy protection.

- Support data backup, simply to create an account with Dfox and import your local data.

- You always own your assets. Dfox has no access to your private keys. It is totally secure and saft to use.

[Coming soon...]

- DeFi protocols about to support: InstaDapp, Token Sets, bZx, Harvest and etc.

- Connect crypto exchanges via API, track and manage balance, holdings and transactions from exchanges. Cryptocurrency exchanges about to support including Binance, Coinbase, Okex, Huobi, ZB, Gate.io, kucoin, Hoo, Bitfinex, FTX, Kraken, Bittrex, Bitstamp, BitMex and more. Stay tuned.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Dfox aims to become the best cryptocurrency management tool. Any problems and feedback, please contact us via the following channels.

Email: info@dfox.cc

Twitter: @dfoxapp

Website:dfox.cc
